---
description: Enforce English language for all PR artifacts and collaboration.
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- All pull request titles, descriptions, commit messages, review comments, and issue discussions MUST be in English.
- When generating summaries or PR bodies, prefer concise, action-oriented English.
- If input is in another language, translate to English before posting externally (keep technical terms intact).
- Use American English spelling (e.g., "behavior", "color").
- Keep headings and bullet points scannable; avoid overly long paragraphs.

